      "patchset_number": 6,
      "line": 1053,
      "message": "If you're going to track a Boolean, then I would suggest using a real boolean value instead of a string.  When using a boolean value, I think it also helps to ensure the value conveys its type ex:  testable or is_testable.  \n\nreqs[key][\"testable\"] = True  (you don't need to use the update method if you're only setting one value.",
